{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium "FAQ Quick Links" section for a luxury Ayurvedic hair wellness brand called Livgenix.
    
    Design Goal:
    Help customers quickly find answers to common questions by directing them to dedicated support pages instead of displaying long FAQ accordions.
    
    Layout:
    - Full-width section.
    - White background.
    - Centered content.
    - Maximum content width: 1400px.
    - Luxury editorial design with generous whitespace.
    
    Header:
    
    Small Eyebrow:
    HELP CENTER
    
    Large Heading:
    Looking for Answers?
    
    Short Description:
    Find quick answers to our most frequently asked questions about orders, shipping, returns, subscriptions, and product guidance.
    
    Below the introduction create a responsive grid of six premium navigation cards.
    
    Card 1
    📦
    Track My Order
    Check your order status and delivery updates.
    
    Button:
    Learn More →
    
    Card 2
    🚚
    Shipping Information
    Delivery timelines, shipping charges and service areas.
    
    Button:
    Learn More →
    
    Card 3
    ↩️
    Returns & Refunds
    Understand our return eligibility and refund process.
    
    Button:
    Learn More →
    
    Card 4
    🌿
    Product Questions
    Learn how to use Livgenix products and choose the right routine.
    
    Button:
    Learn More →
    
    Card 5
    💳
    Payments & Billing
    Accepted payment methods, invoices and transaction support.
    
    Button:
    Learn More →
    
    Card 6
    ❓
    Visit Our FAQ
    Browse all frequently asked questions in one place.
    
    Button:
    View FAQ →
    
    Design Style:
    - Inspired by Aesop, Apple, Ritual and premium wellness brands.
    - White background.
    - Rounded cards (20–24px radius).
    - Thin subtle border (#ECE2CE).
    - No gradients.
    - No heavy shadows.
    - Minimal monochrome line icons.
    - Large spacing between cards.
    - Cards should have a subtle lift animation on hover.
    - Buttons should use a simple text link with a right arrow instead of large filled buttons.
    
    Color Palette:
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Heading: #2F3324
    Accent: #BE9A5C
    Body Text: #6B705C
    Borders: #ECE2CE
    
    The section should feel like a premium customer help center rather than a traditional FAQ block.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-faq-links-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_color }};
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.body_text_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.grid_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border: {{ block.settings.card_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(47, 51, 36, 0.08);
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.card_title_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.card_text_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.body_text_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.link_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    transition: gap 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .ai-faq-links-card-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-faq-links-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap | times: 0.75 }}px;
    }

    .ai-faq-links-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-faq-links-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-faq-links-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 990px) {
    .ai-faq-links-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-faq-links-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-faq-links-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-faq-links-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.eyebrow != blank %}
        <div class="ai-faq-links-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.eyebrow }}</div>
